{"tid":767663,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想去中國，搵間青年旅社避世，有咩選擇？","createTime":"2018-08-04T16:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T07:46:24.000Z","uid":357,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"391d3dcd64e4599d71f5789b61f8619ab231e955","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"想比較偏僻<br />\n唔好離香港太遠<br />\n費事嘥錢坐飛機所以先會揀中國<br />\n廣東省或者鄰近嘅省有冇啲三四線嘅城市，可以安安靜靜咁過返兩個星期<br />\n就算附近乜都冇，得啲山山水水都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 如果我係五毛奶共，都會打大陸同內地，而唔打中國啦<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7015c1ddea599ab59be6f0020bd8eba3084fda7d","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"3 4 線我都唔識<br />\n西安我有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4802f91322327900dcb4d8fe905cab5c2df1bc89","tid":767663,"uid":35228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"台灣啦"},{"pid":"7d85b7208b3e440d08ebdb08e38bec6450e5a6bf","tid":767663,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"出左廣東省，坐高鐵會貴過坐飛機去台灣<br />\n除非你去廣西，或者搭巴士"},{"pid":"db216d72e91f2189f8b34686d2d03b399cc4e4be","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7015c1ddea599ab59be6f0020bd8eba3084fda7d","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"3 4 線我都唔識<br />\n西安我有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"西安去過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd55bd006a5908dca10abe5eb6a3558f5866b547","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"4802f91322327900dcb4d8fe905cab5c2df1bc89","tid":767663,"uid":35228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"台灣啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"唔想晒千幾蚊搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw thx"},{"pid":"7e58a0a40c7a0de09628e8cf3ef8041be740d549","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d85b7208b3e440d08ebdb08e38bec6450e5a6bf","tid":767663,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"出左廣東省，坐高鐵會貴過坐飛機去台灣<br />\n除非你去廣西，或者搭巴士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"已經做足瞓火車嘅準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住坐慢車"},{"pid":"0ecc726d75dccd54162d73d411a6ae12f100dcab","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"桂林點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caedcdbb678b316eb103fb63cb4683cbca41c6f","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"青旅揀好啲 有啲無氣氛<br />\n有啲會一班人或出去玩"},{"pid":"4b933bd13758b3be2c48c3eedded2ef705f0e981","tid":767663,"uid":193131,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:10:25.000Z","msg":"行政拘留15日夠唔夠避世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632aba9d1e832b0fe53c7df1386d8bd234f970b8","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3caedcdbb678b316eb103fb63cb4683cbca41c6f","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"青旅揀好啲 有啲無氣氛<br />\n有啲會一班人或出去玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"我知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 住過一啲同酒店一樣模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7010fa9e199f55c8900a6979b4ca427b24f71e9","tid":767663,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"三四線點會有青年旅社<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青年旅社嘅存在就係因為住宿貴+多人去<br />\n你估旅遊點/一線支那城市消費又會平過台灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1274998b6fd06b01363b3be0814d4fea6126b1f1","tid":767663,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ecc726d75dccd54162d73d411a6ae12f100dcab","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"桂林點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"你想避世之嘛，去深圳是但搵間青旅，反正避世都唔預你出街架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n桂林其實消費都唔平，隨左車費，乜都要比錢，d景點得座山仔，行幾個鐘都好似成百蚊<br />\n同埋市區外既景點都好遠，一坐車出去講緊要夜晚先返到黎"},{"pid":"62ef2dfaf7f2338558fefdc6a52162e84fd0e9ae","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"632aba9d1e832b0fe53c7df1386d8bd234f970b8","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3caedcdbb678b316eb103fb63cb4683cbca41c6f","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"青旅揀好啲 有啲無氣氛<br />\n有啲會一班人或出去玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"我知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 住過一啲同酒店一樣模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"氣氛好既夜晚一齊玩killer<br />\n再出去食個宵夜<br />\n住番一兩個星期絕對無問題"},{"pid":"6e55cb00aac3b72849913bebf056746adffdf363","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ef2dfaf7f2338558fefdc6a52162e84fd0e9ae","tid":767663,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislik