 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"你想避世之嘛，去深圳是但搵間青旅，反正避世都唔預你出街架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n桂林其實消費都唔平，隨左車費，乜都要比錢，d景點得座山仔，行幾個鐘都好似成百蚊<br />\n同埋市區外既景點都好遠，一坐車出去講緊要夜晚先返到黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"thx先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係咁，諗梗長沙張家界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:28:26.000Z","msg":"如果去左張家界先，有機會去桂林你會對桂林會好失望，所以我覺得去左桂林先會更好<br />\n<br />\n點都好啦，你自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n張家界基本上消費都好貴，車費當然比桂林更貴，同埋坐高鐵都真係覺得辛苦，唔好講巴士"},{"pid":"852573e5b7fcf4cad64c914b2ed0629596d185c1","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ba0499520e0a609779d642553655b634b90478","tid":767663,"uid":184745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"洱海/瀘沽湖租間青旅幾日掂唔掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"幾掂，但遠，同埋嗰頭都去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c662ace5361f4ce400a4b59b8a601abcb05bede","tid":767663,"uid":176306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"雲南香格里拉會唔會考慮？<br />\n<br />\n好正！天氣好好，個天藍到你以為係p上去嘅，大草原有馬牛羊。住當地民宿，食當地野，認真係遠離城市<br />\n<br />\n但我已經係16年去架啦，到宜家都仲好掛住<br />\n<br />\n不過要講返香格里拉可能會有高原反應，但好睇人"},{"pid":"ec345e858bf0ff2fe4041bcc52f669dcfd8b5527","tid":767663,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98d034340729239a503c577c33c43a4e8e087dfb","tid":767663,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1274998b6fd06b01363b3be0814d4fea6126b1f1","tid":767663,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ecc726d75dccd54162d73d411a6ae12f100dcab","tid"